Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.06,0:00:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫谷山麻衣 高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做着狩灵师的兼职
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天 在我打工的事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉谷shibuya psychic research
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称SPR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了一位森下典子小姐 委托我们调查一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶到森下家一看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是家具无缘无故地移动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来厨房又突然起火
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是灵在搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子小姐的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美有可能是引起吵闹鬼现象的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是更可疑的是人偶美美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听礼美说美美会说话后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想验证一下真假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:01:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家被人偶诅咒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,档案 2     {\r}{\u1}{\fs40}玩偶之家{\r}  {\fs35}#2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和开始看到时一样坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵和器械的性质不合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得礼美不能再和美美在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里的都是坏魔女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也是魔女的爪牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美觉得姐姐还是留下来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好把她们解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的 你一定要乖乖的听我的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚你在和谁说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有美美？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚我明明关上门了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概我被讨厌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些朋友是从什么时候来玩的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.66,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美和他们关系好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美美带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这屋子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是附近有名的鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来 我倒觉得美美有问题 不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说过那些看不到的朋友 是美美带来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是灵附在美美身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用美美在搞鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许有这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要试着吓它一下?和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 终于到本大爷出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:16.82,zhouwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唵苏婆你苏婆　吽缚曰罗吽发吒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚除灵期间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美身边由绫子守着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚踝脱臼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有人用力拉住我的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩的手印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美我先保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把关于美美所有的事都告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把美美还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美什么时候开始说话的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是礼美的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,典子受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美美干的 不是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吼她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这么小的孩子搞哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美说不能对其他人说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和其他人好她就会欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美什么时候开始说话的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这儿以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 美美 很棒的房子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是坏魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是魔女的手下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人要杀死礼美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也是魔女那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对的 你不能和任何人好噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你违反了约定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果礼美忘了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和姐姐一起玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美就会把东西藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者把房子搞乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是违背约定的惩罚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后美美就带了其他朋友来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来了很多孩子 都跟我差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是美美的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是美美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是以前的主人病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂附在它身上了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才讨厌人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为不是美美的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到现在还这么说么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶只是被当作容器使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有灵被困在这幢宅子里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它到底是谁...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想办法找出它的正体的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美就有危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美就危险？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（坏孩子要受惩罚）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美说出了被告知不能说出的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美认为礼美背叛了她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要离开礼美一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在清除那个字迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要干这种活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不要让礼美看到那些字迹的是小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他还真有一点点体贴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦 就那家伙来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 和尚...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:29.93,zhouwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唵苏婆你苏婆　吽缚曰罗吽发吒弱吽梵斛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把美美处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 对不起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 典子你才更不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连香奈女士也离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么恐怖的房子我住不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 脚还痛么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美肯跟我好好相处的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛就会飞走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美去给你摘花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣姐走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.66,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘哪一朵呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最漂亮的那朵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拔不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 拦住她！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有个池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒子烧得干干净净
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你毫发无损啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 不要生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要欺负我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美 在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美 礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是美美的报复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是惩罚？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定要搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也许会好些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些吵闹鬼是即使你搬家也会跟过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！那你让我们怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我调查了一下过去这房子的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森下你们来之前是渡边一家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住了三年 因为工作的缘故而把它卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因为发生了奇怪的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再之前是野木一家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿九岁的女儿病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再之前是大沼一家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿住的半年内死了三个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十岁 八岁 七岁的两个男孩一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别死于疾病和意外事故
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再以前 村上家有个十五岁的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更往前 谷口家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这儿玩的亲戚家的十岁男孩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前的池田家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7岁的幺子死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之前立花家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8岁的女儿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在这屋子里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8岁左右的孩子都有危险？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找了这方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开这房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请至少等到他们来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人偶绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有这样的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的灵附在她所疼爱的人偶身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家里走来走去什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶本身应该没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这房子的地缚灵附在人偶身上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自澳洲的驱魔者 约翰·布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和灵媒师原真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人也是来协助调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可怕的鬼屋还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在想什么呢 真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的灵到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边哭边说想回妈妈身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房子在聚集着灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是小孩子的灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初 产生了语言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言与神同在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言即是神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么样我先为她祈祷过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该会好一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 涉谷君 人偶呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 美美不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一没留神就...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 麦克风里有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小孩子的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在找礼美的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰干的活有效了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 结界也许有用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用咒语让恶灵无法进入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我注意到礼美脚边的棉被鼓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掀开一看 它就在那儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼美没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音突然消失是因为找到了礼美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天国之父 允许我以你之名祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望的神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请怜悯我们 赐予我们繁荣兴旺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请注视我们 永在我们头顶照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初 产生了语言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言与神同在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言即是神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光在暗之中闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而暗却不理解光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得灵已经除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让它再被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:17:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把它烧了比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次美美很轻易地被烧掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为美美的正体是这个房子里的地缚灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是死在这房子里的孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才把那些到这儿来的孩子们当朋友 要带走他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那些孩子也变成了地缚灵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么都是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它是寂寞的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找可以代替母亲的典子、麻衣她们不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 美美却尝试着要把她们排除出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 原小姐的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来好像还是不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除灵看看吧 和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初死去的孩子立花雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她的生殁时间和法名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗派是净土宗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查的真清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,70年前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看一下这之前的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真够有自信的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的只要搬到宾馆就可以了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个护身符会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了安全起见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松崎和约翰会跟你们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣姐不去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原小姐 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵们没察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符起作用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开工了吧
