Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:09.56,zhouwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唵苏婆你苏婆　吽缚曰罗吽发吒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度开始下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是床附近...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经降低二度左右
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克风呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是竟没有杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始出现“鬼音”了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有敲击声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋 客厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林 客厅的温度？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是零下两度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零下？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚 不是那间房
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来事情的根源在客厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客厅？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开走开走开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚的曼陀罗经让这些孩子们很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样...
